data.description: Welcome to this charming one-level home with 1705 sqft of living space, ft. 3 beds and 1.5 baths. The layout is thoughtfully designed with the kitchen at the center of the home, allowing for easy access and a seamless flow. This home truly lives large, with an open and inviting atmosphere that is perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. Through the light filled French doors you will discover a covered BBQ area. The enclosed back porch offers space for keeping your belongings protected from the elements, while the large semi-finished attic provides endless possibilities for customization and expansion. Convenience, comfort, and versatility are the hallmarks of this property. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
